&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;with-caption&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#with-caption&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; With caption&lt;/h3&gt;
